# laravel

> AGENTS.md: instructions for AI coding agents working on this project.
> Human contributors: see README.md.

## Stack

- PHP
- Laravel

## Commands

(no commands detected. Fill in the commands agents should run for build, test, lint, etc.)

## Conventions

- PSR-12 coding style. Composer for dependencies. PHP 8+ typed properties.
- Validate with Form Request classes; keep controllers focused on HTTP.
- Schema via migrations (`php artisan make:migration`, `php artisan migrate`). Seed with seeders, not ad-hoc scripts.
- Use `php artisan` for every task runner need: migrations, queues, custom commands.

## What to avoid

- `include`/`require` scatter. Use Composer autoloading.
- Inline validation inside controllers when a Form Request fits.

